Test case: verify that all the links under the ul tag are displayed and enabled.
    step1: Open chrome browser
    step2: Navigate to "https://practice.cydeo.com/"
    step3: The title should be "Practice"
    step4: Locate all the links under the ul HTML tag
    step5: Verify there are exactly 50 links
    step6: Verify all the links are visible and clickable 

Here is the xpath locator for locating the links elements that are under the ul tag: 
//ul[@class='list-group']/li/a


Task: verify the next button is visible and clickable
    step1: Open chrome browser
    Step2: Navigate to the URL "https://www.example.com"
    step3: Enter the username in username inputbox
    step4: Enter the password in password inputbox
    step5: Click login button
    step6: verify that user is landed on home page
    step7: verify that the next button on home page is visible and clickable


Task: Send a get request and verify the status code, content-type, json body
    Step 1: Set the base URL to "http://api.example.com"
    Step 2: send a GET request to "/emapleEndPoint"
    Step 3: Verify that status code is 200
    Step 4: Verify that the content-type is application/json
    Step 5: Verify that the id is "A05"
    Step 6: Verify that the firtName is "Josh"
    Step 7: Verify that the lastName is "Jeremy


Task: Send a post request
    Step 1: Set the base URL to "http://api.example.com"
    Step 2: send a POST request to "/emapleEndPoint" with the body:
    {
    "firstname": "Muhtar",
    "lastName": "Mahmut"
    }
    Step 3: Verify that status code is 201
    Step 4: Verify that the content-type is application/json


